{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066370/extras/SteamCustomLogo_610x610.png?t=1723243066\" /><br><br><strong>Grand Gate\u00ae</strong> is a <strong>Tower Defense RPG</strong> with deep combat mechanics set in the fantasy world of Cohr.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066370/extras/Summon.png?t=1723243066\" /><br><br>During your journey in Grand Gate, you will have to choose who is going to compose your <strong>tower roster</strong>. With a total of <strong>25 unique towers</strong> split between <strong>legends</strong> and <strong>pawns</strong>, you're sure to find a strategy that suits your playstyle!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066370/extras/Defend.png?t=1723243066\" /><br><br>The world of Cohr needs to be defended from all kinds of enemies. <strong>Explore</strong> the universe of Grand Gate by playing <strong>60+ carefully handcrafted maps</strong> with unique challenges and several types of combat strategies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066370/extras/Discover.png?t=1723243066\" /><br><br>Embrace your <strong>purpose</strong>. <strong>Protect</strong> the people of Cohr from the coming dark.<br>Being a <strong>commander</strong> is not an easy task to do, you need to find your allies and prepare to fight against different enemies. <strong>Customize</strong> your towers, <strong>create</strong> various strategies, <strong>experience</strong> challenging gameplay and <strong>discover</strong> the secrets of Grand Gate.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066370/extras/Creativity.png?t=1723243066\" /><br><br>In Grand Gate, combat is defined by a set of rules and elements denominated as the <strong